description:
Nominated for Best Dating App by About.com 
 

Chat instantly with people near you right from the palm of your hand. Unlock special rewards just for using the app. 
Play the newest version and increase your opportunity for more real-time interactions with real people! 

By downloading the free SpeedDate app, you can: 
• Signup from your iPhone, iPad, or iPod touch for FREE. 
• Upload photos from your phone or from your Facebook account. 
• Send Winks to your matches for FREE. 
• Search for local singles for FREE. 
• Favorite your matches for FREE. 
• Chat with your matches!
• Earn coins to unlock special flirting powers. 

Get the most out of your SpeedDate experience by upgrading to a premium membership. As a premium member you can get: 
• Unlimited access to “Likes Me” which let you see who’s viewed your profile and who Favorited you. 
• Receive up to 8,000 coins that can be used towards sending SpeedFlirts and becoming a Featured Member. 
• Unlimited email with other members. 
• Higher priority in search. 
• Full access to SpeedDate.com or Facebook.com/Speeddate. 

You have four subscription plans to choose from: 
• $15.83/month for 12 months. 
• $26.67/month for 6 months. 
• $30.00/month for 3 months. 
• $39.99 for a one month subscription.

Please remember that when you subscribe: 
• Your iTunes account will be charged upon confirmation of your purchase and will auto-renew for the same subscription price at the end of each one/three/six/twelve-month period. 
• Auto-renew may be turned off by going to your Account Settings after purchase and must be turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. 
• No cancellation of the current upgrade plan is allowed during your active period. 

What people are saying about SpeedDate: 
“SpeedDate is an online dating service that sets up users on as many 5-minute dates as they want…that’s a good idea!” – Good Morning America 
“If you want fast speed dating to find a date, friend, or lover, the SpeedDate app for iPhone is a great way to accomplish this.” – DatingApps.net 

Other things you need to know: 
• SpeedDate is safe and secure. 
• You can visit us online at www.speeddate.com
• You can view our Privacy Policy at www.speeddate.com/apps/site/views/mp/privacypolicy.php
• You can view our Terms of Use at www.speeddate.com/apps/site/views/mp/termsofuse.php
• You must be at least 18 years old to download and use this app.


Download the free app now and let us show you just how fun it can be to meet new people. We’d also love to hear your feedback on the app – email us at support@speeddate.com
